    "The experimental tools required include Python tools and ChatGPT accounts.",
    "The Python toolkit includes Python installation packages and Matplotlib.",
    "Additionally, to prevent interference among participants and ensure consistent performance and responsiveness when using ChatGPT, this study provided each experimental participant with an independent account for the latest version of ChatGPT from the OpenAI official website.",
    "It is important to note that this research chose Python as the programming language for several reasons.",
    "Firstly, according to the September 2023 TIOBE index (TIOBE, 2023), Python is currently the most popular programming language."
